Stargate.Origins.WEBSpliced.x264-Sporc.mkv

Stargate Origins is a Prequel Low Budget Film taking place in the Stargate Movie Universe with no ties to the SG-1 series franchise.

Synopsis/Plot: A young Catherine Langford embarks on an adventure to unlock the mystery of the Stargate. Catherine and her father examine the gate at a warehouse near Giza. Nazis take them hostage, and reveal they know how to use the gate and force Professor Langford to go through the gate with them.

Originally averaging at 10-13 minutes each, these 10 Episodes are spliced together to create one Feature Length Movie version.

Note, this is not the Feature Cut version that is officially available online! Spin sequences at the end of each mini episode were cut out so there are musical/sound cuttoffs points. There is no enhanced effects nore new introduction title sequence.
